page.title: 09A DAY IN MY LIFE
page.content: My name is Deborah Ann Rooney. I am aged 10 years and 7 months. I have two brothers older than me, my oldest brothers name is Paul Stephen Rooney and he is 18 and my other brother is called David Anthony Rooney and he is 16. I have a pet, Shandy, she is a dog. She is nearly 4. I live at 19 Rutland Road, Wrexham. I go to Victoria Junior Schol and when I am 12 I shall go to Bryn-Offa secondary school. I wake up at a quater to eight, read a book til eight. My school uniform is Navy-Blue with a white shirt and a blue and yellow tie. I have frosties or weetabix for my breakfast, a piece of toast and a drink of five-a-live. I go to school at 8.40 in the car. Our car is a red Escort. When I arrive at school I play in the yard with my friends Cara, Helen, Lucy, Clair, Maija, Kesah,
